[
    {
        "text": "(chopping)",
        "start": 0.183,
        "duration": 0.999
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat music)",
        "start": 1.182,
        "duration": 2.388
    },
    {
        "text": "- Hi, everybody.",
        "start": 3.57,
        "duration": 1.09
    },
    {
        "text": "Check this out.",
        "start": 4.66,
        "duration": 1.29
    },
    {
        "text": "Lots of green onions.",
        "start": 5.95,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "Yesterday, I went to a Korean\ngrocery store in New Jersey",
        "start": 7.48,
        "duration": 4.17
    },
    {
        "text": "and I found really, really big sale.",
        "start": 11.65,
        "duration": 3.09
    },
    {
        "text": "For six bunches, only 1.99.",
        "start": 14.74,
        "duration": 3.74
    },
    {
        "text": "I had to buy.",
        "start": 18.48,
        "duration": 1.09
    },
    {
        "text": "Lot of people have requested this recipe,",
        "start": 19.57,
        "duration": 2.81
    },
    {
        "text": "kimchi made with green onions.",
        "start": 22.38,
        "duration": 3.57
    },
    {
        "text": "Green onion kimchi.",
        "start": 25.95,
        "duration": 1.07
    },
    {
        "text": "In Korean, Pa-kimchi.",
        "start": 27.02,
        "duration": 1.67
    },
    {
        "text": "Pa, how simple it is.",
        "start": 28.69,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "Everybody, say Pa-kimchi (laughs).",
        "start": 30.51,
        "duration": 3.27
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's measure 3 pounds.",
        "start": 33.78,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "So this is 3 pounds.",
        "start": 35.67,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "These guys, I don't need this.",
        "start": 37.89,
        "duration": 2.26
    },
    {
        "text": "When I lived in Korea, the\ngreen onions are thinner.",
        "start": 40.15,
        "duration": 3.26
    },
    {
        "text": "You know, America, some green onions",
        "start": 43.41,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "are kind of a little different.",
        "start": 45.36,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "These are plump and shorter.",
        "start": 46.61,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "And also, so it's always\ncut off like this.",
        "start": 49.28,
        "duration": 3.18
    },
    {
        "text": "So, I just found out how to make",
        "start": 52.46,
        "duration": 2.953
    },
    {
        "text": "green onion kimchi with this.",
        "start": 55.413,
        "duration": 1.937
    },
    {
        "text": "I usually cut into bite-size pieces.",
        "start": 57.35,
        "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
        "text": "These roots, cut off like this.",
        "start": 61.51,
        "duration": 2.47
    },
    {
        "text": "I'll put this in a bowl.",
        "start": 63.98,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Take off the rubber bands.",
        "start": 65.74,
        "duration": 1.593
    },
    {
        "text": "And check out any kind\nof dirty stuff is there.",
        "start": 69.15,
        "duration": 3.443
    },
    {
        "text": "I just cut this way.",
        "start": 73.93,
        "duration": 1.253
    },
    {
        "text": "You see, this tip part,",
        "start": 77.979,
        "duration": 3.081
    },
    {
        "text": "it's already cut off,",
        "start": 81.06,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "but it's kind of dirty-looking.",
        "start": 82.65,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "I like to remove this.",
        "start": 85.09,
        "duration": 1.633
    },
    {
        "text": "Why did I collect this?",
        "start": 93.148,
        "duration": 3.012
    },
    {
        "text": "This is going to be a\nreally good ingredients",
        "start": 96.16,
        "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
        "text": "when you make a delicious stock.",
        "start": 99.06,
        "duration": 1.79
    },
    {
        "text": "You can add this to anchovy-kelp stock",
        "start": 100.85,
        "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
        "text": "or a vegetable stock.",
        "start": 103.35,
        "duration": 1.48
    },
    {
        "text": "And I'm going to wash this.",
        "start": 104.83,
        "duration": 2.734
    },
    {
        "text": "(water splashing)",
        "start": 107.564,
        "duration": 2.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Rinse and drain, rinse and drain",
        "start": 113.286,
        "duration": 2.394
    },
    {
        "text": "around 3 times, until there's no dirt.",
        "start": 115.68,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "Shake it, shake it,",
        "start": 120.74,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "to remove all this excess\nwater and put this back.",
        "start": 122.36,
        "duration": 4.173
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm going to season this with fish sauce.",
        "start": 127.78,
        "duration": 2.81
    },
    {
        "text": "Making Pa-kimchi is very easy",
        "start": 130.59,
        "duration": 2.03
    },
    {
        "text": "compared to Napa cabbage kimchi,",
        "start": 132.62,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "because I don't need garlic,",
        "start": 134.84,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "because this has already its own spicy flavor.",
        "start": 137.02,
        "duration": 3.11
    },
    {
        "text": "So I don't need to add garlic or ginger,",
        "start": 140.13,
        "duration": 3.81
    },
    {
        "text": "radish or other stuff, I\ndon't need anything else.",
        "start": 143.94,
        "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
        "text": "When I lived in Korea,",
        "start": 146.68,
        "duration": 1.67
    },
    {
        "text": "I used real fermented anchovies.",
        "start": 148.35,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Just fermented anchovies, after boiling it,",
        "start": 151.35,
        "duration": 3.45
    },
    {
        "text": "strained it, removed\nall the fish bones,",
        "start": 154.8,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "and then let it cool down and I use it.",
        "start": 157.6,
        "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm showing you easy way,",
        "start": 160.3,
        "duration": 2.26
    },
    {
        "text": "how to make this kimchi.",
        "start": 162.56,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "Fish sauce, 1 cup.",
        "start": 164.0,
        "duration": 1.85
    },
    {
        "text": "Pa-kimchi should be salty and it has its own unique taste.",
        "start": 165.85,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "So we got to add \na lot of fish sauce.",
        "start": 168.65,
        "duration": 3.22
    },
    {
        "text": "And then I'm going to mix this.",
        "start": 171.87,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "(water splashing)",
        "start": 182.05,
        "duration": 2.833
    },
    {
        "text": "By the way, if you are vegetarian,",
        "start": 185.75,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "instead of a fish sauce, use soy sauce,",
        "start": 187.7,
        "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, let's make a kimchi paste.",
        "start": 190.86,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "3 cups of water.",
        "start": 193.19,
        "duration": 1.463
    },
    {
        "text": "And this is glutinous\nrice flour, 1/4 cup.",
        "start": 196.62,
        "duration": 4.507
    },
    {
        "text": "Then turn on the heat,",
        "start": 202.7,
        "duration": 1.373
    },
    {
        "text": "to medium high heat.",
        "start": 205.54,
        "duration": 1.153
    },
    {
        "text": "(beater clinking)",
        "start": 208.014,
        "duration": 1.776
    },
    {
        "text": "I just whisk this.",
        "start": 209.79,
        "duration": 2.133
    },
    {
        "text": "Occasionally, stir this\nuntil this is all cooked.",
        "start": 213.1,
        "duration": 4.31
    },
    {
        "text": "A couple of years ago, my\nmom, me, and my sister,",
        "start": 217.41,
        "duration": 3.91
    },
    {
        "text": "we went to picnic, all day picnic.",
        "start": 221.32,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Of course, we had to make some lunchbox.",
        "start": 224.36,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "In Los Angeles, \nKorean grocery stores sell",
        "start": 226.92,
        "duration": 3.87
    },
    {
        "text": "all kinds of delicious side dishes,",
        "start": 230.79,
        "duration": 2.26
    },
    {
        "text": "they're not very expensive.",
        "start": 233.05,
        "duration": 1.51
    },
    {
        "text": "Kimchi, we had to choose 1 kind of kimchi.",
        "start": 234.56,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "We, three of us, looked at each other.",
        "start": 237.08,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Pa-kimchi, so that's it!",
        "start": 239.32,
        "duration": 2.03
    },
    {
        "text": "Pa-kimchi is really\ndelicious and pungent,",
        "start": 241.35,
        "duration": 3.22
    },
    {
        "text": "and if you love it, you are\nsupposed to keep eating it. ",
        "start": 244.57,
        "duration": 3.48
    },
    {
        "text": "Everybody loves it.",
        "start": 248.05,
        "duration": 2.19
    },
    {
        "text": "Anyway, my family, you\nknow, we love Pa-kimchi.",
        "start": 250.24,
        "duration": 3.851
    },
    {
        "text": "Look at that, bubbles are popping up.",
        "start": 254.091,
        "duration": 3.352
    },
    {
        "text": "And still, color is white.",
        "start": 257.443,
        "duration": 2.667
    },
    {
        "text": "And then I'm going to add\nsugar, 2 tablespoons.",
        "start": 260.11,
        "duration": 4.153
    },
    {
        "text": "Just keep stirring.",
        "start": 268.26,
        "duration": 1.71
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm going to turn down the heat to medium,",
        "start": 269.97,
        "duration": 3.03
    },
    {
        "text": "and keep stirring,",
        "start": 273.0,
        "duration": 0.9
    },
    {
        "text": "until it's a little bit translucent.",
        "start": 275.305,
        "duration": 3.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Maybe some of you guys will say,",
        "start": 280.74,
        "duration": 1.207
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Oh, Maangchi, the color of\nis light brown.\"",
        "start": 281.947,
        "duration": 3.603
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, this is organic cane sugar.",
        "start": 285.55,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "You can use\na brown or white sugar, too.",
        "start": 288.19,
        "duration": 3.083
    },
    {
        "text": "See, this consistency?",
        "start": 292.72,
        "duration": 2.043
    },
    {
        "text": "Translucent.",
        "start": 297.32,
        "duration": 1.41
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, turn off.",
        "start": 298.73,
        "duration": 1.403
    },
    {
        "text": "All I have to do is to wait until",
        "start": 308.04,
        "duration": 2.89
    },
    {
        "text": "these green onions are nicely salted",
        "start": 310.93,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "and my porridge is totally cooled down.",
        "start": 313.6,
        "duration": 4.19
    },
    {
        "text": "So, see you soon.",
        "start": 317.79,
        "duration": 1.083
    },
    {
        "text": "I salted it for 1 hour, ",
        "start": 324.07,
        "duration": 4.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Every 20 minutes, I turned over.",
        "start": 328.37,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm going to strain this.",
        "start": 331.13,
        "duration": 2.393
    },
    {
        "text": "I cooled down thoroughly.",
        "start": 340.11,
        "duration": 1.633
    },
    {
        "text": "And add here.",
        "start": 343.13,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "We can add this Gochugaru,\nhot pepper flakes.",
        "start": 346.96,
        "duration": 3.872
    },
    {
        "text": "That's it, that's all \nwe need to add.",
        "start": 350.832,
        "duration": 3.568
    },
    {
        "text": "So 1 1/2 cup.",
        "start": 354.4,
        "duration": 1.35
    },
    {
        "text": "I came from Jeolla province from Korea.",
        "start": 355.75,
        "duration": 2.68
    },
    {
        "text": "Pa-kimchi from Korean Jeolla province",
        "start": 358.43,
        "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
        "text": "is that we use really\nthick and heavy paste.",
        "start": 361.01,
        "duration": 3.65
    },
    {
        "text": "It should be really red and spicy.",
        "start": 364.66,
        "duration": 2.57
    },
    {
        "text": "So I add 1 1/2 cup\nKorean hot pepper flakes.",
        "start": 367.23,
        "duration": 3.34
    },
    {
        "text": "One and half cup.",
        "start": 370.57,
        "duration": 1.463
    },
    {
        "text": "And mix it all together.",
        "start": 373.77,
        "duration": 1.453
    },
    {
        "text": "Sooner or later, this\npaste will get thickened",
        "start": 380.66,
        "duration": 2.99
    },
    {
        "text": "because these hot pepper flakes",
        "start": 383.65,
        "duration": 1.877
    },
    {
        "text": "are going to soaked into this porridge.",
        "start": 385.527,
        "duration": 3.203
    },
    {
        "text": "So you can wait for 30 minutes,",
        "start": 388.73,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "30 minutes after, \nthese hot pepper flakes",
        "start": 391.06,
        "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
        "text": "are well, well soaked and incorporated",
        "start": 393.56,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "very nicely to creamy paste.",
        "start": 395.86,
        "duration": 2.51
    },
    {
        "text": "But I'm busy, so just\nonly 5 minutes after,",
        "start": 398.37,
        "duration": 3.37
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm going to mix this all together.",
        "start": 401.74,
        "duration": 2.053
    },
    {
        "text": "Looks nice and juicy.",
        "start": 422.71,
        "duration": 2.023
    },
    {
        "text": "We made the Pa-kimchi today.",
        "start": 453.07,
        "duration": 1.97
    },
    {
        "text": "This is so delicious-looking, isn't it?",
        "start": 455.04,
        "duration": 2.39
    },
    {
        "text": "Juicy and red.",
        "start": 457.43,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "I know exactly\nwhat it tastes like",
        "start": 459.77,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "because I have been using\nthis recipe for a long time.",
        "start": 462.37,
        "duration": 3.32
    },
    {
        "text": "I really enjoy fresh\nkimchi, but just you can ferment it.",
        "start": 465.69,
        "duration": 3.75
    },
    {
        "text": "After it's fermented, it tastes sour,",
        "start": 469.44,
        "duration": 2.27
    },
    {
        "text": "that's also really yummy, delicious.",
        "start": 471.71,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "So you can ferment\noutside the refrigerator.",
        "start": 473.93,
        "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
        "text": "It takes longer than Napa cabbage kimchi.",
        "start": 477.17,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "It depends on your room temperature.",
        "start": 479.81,
        "duration": 2.14
    },
    {
        "text": "If your room temperature is high, warm,",
        "start": 481.95,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "it's going to be fermented so quickly.",
        "start": 485.23,
        "duration": 3.22
    },
    {
        "text": "Otherwise, it takes around 7 days.",
        "start": 488.45,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "When you taste it, it will taste sour.",
        "start": 490.89,
        "duration": 2.07
    },
    {
        "text": "That's fermented kimchi.",
        "start": 492.96,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": "When it's fermented, and\ntransfer to the refrigerator.",
        "start": 494.7,
        "duration": 3.87
    },
    {
        "text": "So keep in the refrigerator\nand always serve cold.",
        "start": 498.57,
        "duration": 4.11
    },
    {
        "text": "So, this kimchi...",
        "start": 509.666,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Let me taste.",
        "start": 514.947,
        "duration": 1.723
    },
    {
        "text": "This spicy pa-kimchi is very special.",
        "start": 516.67,
        "duration": 1.43
    },
    {
        "text": "It's  delicious,",
        "start": 518.1,
        "duration": 4.66
    },
    {
        "text": "but very smelly, the smell lasts\nin your mouth for a long time.",
        "start": 522.76,
        "duration": 4.73
    },
    {
        "text": "So I suggest eating on a weekend,",
        "start": 527.49,
        "duration": 2.78
    },
    {
        "text": "only weekend, Saturday, Sunday.",
        "start": 530.27,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "Monday morning, if yo eat this Pa-kimchi",
        "start": 532.7,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "for breakfast with\nrice?  ",
        "start": 535.52,
        "duration": 3.64
    },
    {
        "text": "The smell is going to be all the hours",
        "start": 539.16,
        "duration": 2.23
    },
    {
        "text": "and hours in your mouth.",
        "start": 541.39,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "You will give people special breath,",
        "start": 542.64,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "green onion breath (laughs).",
        "start": 545.76,
        "duration": 1.577
    },
    {
        "text": "If you want to punish\nsomebody, just go ahead.",
        "start": 548.67,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "But I usually eat it \n165\nfor dinner or just on the weekend.",
        "start": 551.79,
        "duration": 4.03
    },
    {
        "text": "Or anybody, your family\nmembers don't care about",
        "start": 558.01,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "you green onion smell, it's okay, isn't it?",
        "start": 560.83,
        "duration": 2.89
    },
    {
        "text": "It's close enough (chuckles).",
        "start": 563.72,
        "duration": 1.45
    },
    {
        "text": "Mmm.",
        "start": 572.472,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Mmm.",
        "start": 573.305,
        "duration": 0.985
    },
    {
        "text": "Mmm.",
        "start": 574.29,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Fish stew.",
        "start": 575.79,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Whenever I see green onions\non sale at a grocery store,",
        "start": 578.87,
        "duration": 3.65
    },
    {
        "text": "it reminds me of my friend,",
        "start": 582.52,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "old friend, Mrs. Yu-yi, she's Chinese.",
        "start": 584.41,
        "duration": 3.8
    },
    {
        "text": "I met her in Missouri.",
        "start": 588.21,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "When I studied at the ESL class,",
        "start": 590.13,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "she was one of my classmates.",
        "start": 592.37,
        "duration": 2.23
    },
    {
        "text": "One day, the school has a\npicnic day.",
        "start": 594.6,
        "duration": 3.53
    },
    {
        "text": "All classmates and everybody ",
        "start": 598.13,
        "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
        "text": "went to picnic. \nShe came to my house",
        "start": 601.29,
        "duration": 3.22
    },
    {
        "text": "to go together with me.",
        "start": 604.51,
        "duration": 2.39
    },
    {
        "text": "She saw my kimchi containers in my refrigerator,",
        "start": 606.9,
        "duration": 3.35
    },
    {
        "text": "huge kimchi containers in my refrigerator.",
        "start": 610.25,
        "duration": 3.7
    },
    {
        "text": "Her eyes were like getting\nbigger and bigger.",
        "start": 613.95,
        "duration": 2.398
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Wooo, you made this amount?\"",
        "start": 616.348,
        "duration": 2.382
    },
    {
        "text": "She also saw green onion\nkimchi.",
        "start": 618.73,
        "duration": 3.5
    },
    {
        "text": "She was so surprised.",
        "start": 622.23,
        "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Later,",
        "start": 624.73,
        "duration": 2.92
    },
    {
        "text": "a few months later, she called me,",
        "start": 627.65,
        "duration": 2.167
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Hey, now \nthis grocery store is having ",
        "start": 629.817,
        "duration": 3.653
    },
    {
        "text": "a big sale, green onions,\nso I just let you know.\"",
        "start": 633.47,
        "duration": 3.37
    },
    {
        "text": "What a nice person! ",
        "start": 636.84,
        "duration": 1.63
    },
    {
        "text": "She knew that I sometimes \nmake green onion kimchi.",
        "start": 638.47,
        "duration": 3.94
    },
    {
        "text": "So I need a lot of green onions,",
        "start": 642.41,
        "duration": 1.73
    },
    {
        "text": "but I'm a frugal housewife.",
        "start": 644.14,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "So she just thought, \"Okay,\nthis is good information for her.\"",
        "start": 646.47,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "I really miss her.",
        "start": 650.15,
        "duration": 1.29
    },
    {
        "text": "She went back to her hometown, China,",
        "start": 651.44,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "Her husband was working\nat Tianjin university,",
        "start": 654.19,
        "duration": 2.93
    },
    {
        "text": "but we just a couple of times\nkept in touch, you know,",
        "start": 657.12,
        "duration": 2.99
    },
    {
        "text": "such as Christmas, you know, time passes.",
        "start": 660.11,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "I also lost contact with her.",
        "start": 662.43,
        "duration": 3.49
    },
    {
        "text": "So, while you are living,\nyou know,",
        "start": 665.92,
        "duration": 3.01
    },
    {
        "text": "especially, certain time\nin your life when you met some friends",
        "start": 668.93,
        "duration": 3.86
    },
    {
        "text": " who influenced me,\nor I influenced them,",
        "start": 672.79,
        "duration": 4.13
    },
    {
        "text": "At that time, we were\njust really close friends,",
        "start": 676.92,
        "duration": 3.59
    },
    {
        "text": "but you know,\nlife is all complicated.",
        "start": 680.51,
        "duration": 3.89
    },
    {
        "text": "We sometimes have ups and down,",
        "start": 684.4,
        "duration": 2.77
    },
    {
        "text": "or just, we simply forget the past,",
        "start": 687.17,
        "duration": 4.71
    },
    {
        "text": "but we never forget this kind of good\nmemories. ",
        "start": 691.88,
        "duration": 3.72
    },
    {
        "text": "So I always think about\nher kindness.",
        "start": 695.6,
        "duration": 3.787
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Hey, just now these are on sale.",
        "start": 699.387,
        "duration": 2.183
    },
    {
        "text": "You gotta go there!\" (laughs)",
        "start": 701.57,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "Whenever I see green onions on sale,",
        "start": 703.67,
        "duration": 2.39
    },
    {
        "text": "I think about her, Mrs. Yu-yi.",
        "start": 706.06,
        "duration": 2.81
    },
    {
        "text": "So, today I showed you\nhow to make Pa-kimchi.",
        "start": 708.87,
        "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Enjoy my recipe.",
        "start": 713.11,
        "duration": 1.46
    },
    {
        "text": "See you next time.",
        "start": 714.57,
        "duration": 1.757
    },
    {
        "text": "Bye.",
        "start": 716.327,
        "duration": 0.851
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat music)",
        "start": 717.178,
        "duration": 2.583
    }
]